OL,3,C'A ridiculous situation': Council
OL,4,Ccriticised for painting over potholes
OL,6,FHampshire County Council has been
OL,7,Fcriticised for painting road markings
OL,8,Fover potholes in Basingstoke.
OL,10,FLiberal Democrat Councillor Andy
OL,11,FKonieczko from Basingstoke and Deane
OL,12,FBorough Council says Hampshire County
OL,13,FCouncil carried out works on Sullivan
OL,14,FRoad, near Chalk Ridge Primary School,
OL,15,Fon the last weekend of January.
OL,17,FThe councillor for the Brighton Hill
OL,18,Fward said the council repainted some
OL,19,Froad markings without fixing the
OL,20,Fpotholes.
