OL,3,C'A ridiculous situation': Council
OL,4,Ccriticised for painting over potholes
OL,6,FPosting on social media on Monday 2
OL,7,FFebruary, he said: "We assumed that
OL,8,Fthey were there to repair the huge
OL,9,Fpotholes that had appeared in the area
OL,10,Fin the last few weeks.
OL,12,F"This would have been appreciated by
OL,13,Flocal residents who have had to put up
OL,14,Fwith a terrible road surface when
OL,15,Fdriving on one of Brighton Hill's
OL,16,Fbusiest roads.
OL,18,F"But no - the County Council just
OL,19,Frepainted some road markings without
OL,20,Ffixing the potholes.
