OL,3,C'A ridiculous situation': Council
OL,4,Ccriticised for painting over potholes
OL,6,F"So we've ended up with a ridiculous
OL,7,Fsituation where the new lines have
OL,8,Fbeen painted into the potholes - and
OL,9,Fwill need to be repainted again when
OL,10,Fthe potholes are eventually fixed!"
OL,12,FHe added: "Not only are these potholes
OL,13,Fa huge inconvenience, they're also
OL,14,Fdangerous.
OL,16,F"Drivers are being forced to focus on
OL,17,Fnavigating large holes in the road as
OL,18,Fwell as looking out for other road
OL,19,Fusers and pedestrians. That's worrying
OL,20,F- particularly when there's a school
OL,21,Fnearby."
