OL,3,C'A ridiculous situation': Council
OL,4,Ccriticised for painting over potholes
OL,6,FHampshire County Council has since
OL,7,Frepaired some of the potholes.
OL,9,FA Hampshire County Council
OL,10,Fspokesperson said: "These school road
OL,11,Fmarkings were completed as part of a
OL,12,Fwider programme of lining works.
OL,14,F"Recent weather conditions have caused
OL,15,Froad defects to appear more rapidly
OL,16,Facross the county, and in some cases,
OL,17,Fissues develop after works are
OL,18,Fscheduled but before they take place.
